-- ft.page: /add-package/ API

A new package would be added by `/add-package/` api.

-- ft.h1: Input

-- ft.h2: `name`

Name of the package.

-- ft.h2: `git`

Git URL of the package.

Note: can we easily do a git check?

-- ft.h2: `plan`

Plan for the package. Can be either `free` or `paid` only.

-- ft.h1: Side Effect: update nginx

This calls adds the initial `<domain>.conf` for nginx. For initial configuration
it makes nginx point to django.
